Entries.default: "Save your mischief for Queen's Berth, outsider. One wrong step and we'll have you over the side of the falls."
"The trading companies have sent emissaries to speak with our queen. Hylea blesses her with patience."
"Watch your step. The mist makes the stones slick."
"You are a guest here, Watcher. Do not forget it."
"They say Tangaloa speaks through you, Watcher. Is that true?"
"Are those not the Brass Citadel cannons?"
